44
00:03:03,966 --> 00:03:06,500
Here's what I'll cover today:

45
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:10,300
A quick overview of StoreKit APIs

46
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:15,233
Our implementation context and strategic decisions

47
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:18,466
The technical challenges we faced

48
00:03:18,766 --> 00:03:21,766
The tools we used for testing

49
00:03:22,366 --> 00:03:25,733
The App Store review process reality

50
00:03:25,833 --> 00:03:28,400
And key takeaways

51
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:31,533
Alright, let’s start with something fun.

52
00:03:31,533 --> 00:03:35,300
 Can I ask everyone  to raise your hand up?

53
00:03:35,300 --> 00:03:37,300
 Yes, everyone.

54
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:38,633
 Thank you very much.

55
00:03:38,633 --> 00:03:40,766
 Now, Keep your hand up ...

56
00:03:40,766 --> 00:03:45,833
if you know which In-App Purchase framework your company is  using

57
00:03:45,833 --> 00:03:46,766
 If you don't know,

58
